### **3. 27_LogRippleTrace**  
**Description:**  
Detects repetition ripples and sudden bursts in system logs based on time and frequency shifts.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogRippleTrace - Spike-Aware Log Analyzer

LogRippleTrace identifies recurring error patterns and ripple-effect bursts that may indicate system failure or overload.

## Features
- Frequency + burst clustering  
- Timeline correlation  
- Simple keyword filters  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/27_LogRippleTrace.git
cd 27_LogRippleTrace
python analyze.py
